<HEAD>Furnace Fumes _ Silent Killer Wipes Out Four Relatives</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By JAMES A. CARLSON</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>MILWAUKEE (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
