<FIRST>s e BC-BroadwayTix Adv21-22   01-17 0587</FIRST>
<SECOND>BC-Broadway Tix, Adv 21-22,0605</SECOND>
<HEAD>$Adv21</HEAD>
<HEAD>$Adv22</HEAD>
<HEAD>For Release Weekend Editions, Jan. 21-22, and Thereafter</HEAD>
<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
