<HEAD>Precede LONDON</HEAD>
<HEAD>Eds: New throughout with new findings</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By DAVID BRISCOE</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
